title: ID_Object_RuinedDoll_Seen_ENG
---
Daniel: <Italic>There's a rag doll on the desk, and it's surrounded by books and notebooks.</> #tone:neutral
Daniel: <Italic>Why does Melissa keep it here? Does it help her focus? Or maybe it's a doll capable of doing homework...?</> #tone:question
Daniel: <Italic>No, it's not the time to joke around. Better ask Melissa.</> #tone:serious
===

title: ID_Object_RuinedDoll_AlreadySeen_ENG
---
Daniel: <Italic>A strange doll in a strange place. Better ask about it to the owner.</> #tone:neutral
