title: ID_Object_MaryLighter_Collected_ENG
tag: EventFlags.Mary.Dialogues.AtHome.Completed
---
Daniel: <Italic>That looks like a lighter ornated with some letters.</> #tone:thinking
Daniel: <Italic>A lighter under the bed of a man died in a fire. Mmh...</> #tone:thinking
Daniel: <Italic>I'm starting to doubt it merely "fell" here.</> #tone:serious
Daniel: <Italic>I need to talk to Mary.</> #tone:serious
<<SetTag EventFlags.MaryLighter.PickedUp true>>
===
//FINE


