---
Daniel: <Italic>It's not really believable that the lighter was found on the crime scene.</> #tone:thinking
Daniel: <Italic>It should be dented. I need to find a way to ruin it.</> #tone:serious
Daniel: <Italic>Mmh... Maybe cake isn't the only thing paper towels are useful for.</> #tone:serious
